research_municipality_step.notes: Commerce, TX operates under a council-manager form of government, which is a variation of the mayor-council system. The Mayor and four council members are elected at-large. Teddy Reel was re-elected as Mayor in May 2025. There was conflicting information regarding the Mayor and Place 3 Council Member between the city's staff directory and the Texas Municipal League directory; the TML directory and recent election results were prioritized for accuracy.
